OL,5, Former sub-postmaster Alan Bates says  
OL,6, he will consider raising funds for     
OL,7, private prosecutions of Post Office    
OL,8, bosses over the Horizon IT scandal.    
OL,10,FHe told the BBC he would act if the    
OL,11,Fauthorities did not take cases forward.
OL,13,F"It was fine when the Post Office      
OL,14,Fbrought private prosecutions, so if    
OL,15,Fwe've got to do it in return so be it",
OL,16,Fhe said.                               
OL,18,FMore than 900 sub-postmasters were     
OL,19,Fwrongly prosecuted for shortfalls      
OL,20,Fcaused by faulty Horizon software.     
